Class IloCplex.LongParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.Param
      • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.LongParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.LongParam
extends IloCplex.Param
    Symbolic parameter names for integer-valued IloCplex parameters. For more detail about each parameter, see the CPLEX Parameters Reference Manual.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
